data.description: Price adjustment alert! Don't miss this great house on this quiet cul-de-sac street. Owner hates to leave but has been relocated. Hardwood floors, separate formal dining - chandelier to remain. Formal living room with hardwoods. Great room with gas log fireplace. Kitchen has great counter space and lots of storage. Breakfast area and breakfast bar. Some brand-new appliances, including refrigerator, that will remain. New sink. New paint throughout. New HVAC. Carpets have been professionally cleaned. Separate laundry room and additional room that could be an office or craft room. Deck has grill that is piped to the gas line and the backyard is fenced in with tons of privacy! Make it yours today!
